Package: infercnvpip
Title: InferCNV Pipeline for Single-Cell Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miu Shing", family = "Hung", email = "matthewhungms@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-0412-4374"))
Description: Provides a streamlined interface to the InferCNV package for analyzing copy number
    variations in single-cell RNA-seq data. This package simplifies the workflow for running
    InferCNV on Seurat objects.
